data.description:
You don't see many homes like this in Shingle Creek! 1924 build with a large addition done in the early 2000s to enlarge bedrooms and add-on the awesome primary suite! 

Loads of natural light throughout, primary ensuite with 2 separate walk-in closets and awesome flex space you could utilize as an office, dressing area, vanity... the choice is yours!

Lots of big-ticket items done for you already! In the last three years the furnace, sewer line, and washing machine replaced, gutter shields and oak fence added! 

Steps away from Shingle Creek Park which has access to multiple trails that link up to both Creekview Park, the Bubble Bridge, and Lions Park!

Fully-fenced backyard for your two or four-legged friends to enjoy! Generously sized main floor bedrooms with large closets. 

Move right in and enjoy!
